{"tid":2315687,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"68歲兇手被指對性有強烈慾望 1小時喪做千次掌上壓","createTime":"2020-12-07T10:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:34:28.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6bd5b46074f3edef4b2489f2bd4ffa385f2d54","tid":2315687,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412681177913102336715236.jpeg/HhFYfjKOREPCsto65a94i9ijZq7JpYAAtK_lCLSv5Qg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201207%2F412681177913102336715236.jpeg%2FHhFYfjKOREPCsto65a94i9ijZq7JpYAAtK_lCLSv5Qg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=792cd62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓電影《素媛》（又譯︰許願）以2008年「趙斗淳性侵案」為藍本，年僅8歲的受害女童被兇手趙斗淳擄走性侵，導致大小腸流出，終身要依靠人工肛門排洩，殘忍到人神共憤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2725193/org/186e415a753a74129fc1bba468c37573.jpeg/W8NvDR9STRiyssyPQR8OZ2oPB5hAfPiN9RUJjfUVCY0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2725193%2Forg%2F186e415a753a74129fc1bba468c37573.jpeg%2FW8NvDR9STRiyssyPQR8OZ2oPB5hAfPiN9RUJjfUVCY0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f87267d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4205967/org/0131b2094e7fa2bd10408a32c2ae2017.jpg/kjkczAvmOC40TjD1PQ6q45jgq2Dwc524Q8FJdkPBSXY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4205967%2Forg%2F0131b2094e7fa2bd10408a32c2ae2017.jpg%2FkjkczAvmOC40TjD1PQ6q45jgq2Dwc524Q8FJdkPBSXY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=04e13c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2852496/org/ef28ed25b885b028e7ca33dd66f1f8ad.jpeg/G06Ur3l_Pabw6Rx-Zbv2MOb1DxUdQUNsaOkpvmjpKb4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2852496%2Forg%2Fef28ed25b885b028e7ca33dd66f1f8ad.jpeg%2FG06Ur3l_Pabw6Rx-Zbv2MOb1DxUdQUNsaOkpvmjpKb4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b4764ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年趙斗淳被判監12年，轉眼間就出獄在即，眼見這位變態狂魔於本周日（13日）就重獲自由，住其附近的居民都人心惶惶，有消息指受害人因害怕再次面對兇手而搬走，而近日又有報道指趙斗淳體力驚人且性慾過剩，擔心他出獄後會再次犯案。<br />\n<br />\n獄友指趙斗淳在囚時積極健身。（網上圖片）<br />\n獄友指趙斗淳在囚時積極健身。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n有指趙斗淳曾去信法官，態度毫無悔意，更寫下：「有證據就切我性器官！」（影片截圖）<br />\n這宗案件發生於2008年，當年小女孩「素媛」只有8歲，遭到兇手趙鬥淳強逼口交以及強暴。<br />\n受害女童娜英身上有多處傷痕。（《PD手冊》影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據韓國媒體報導，趙斗淳被獄友爆料在囚室中積極健身，現年68歲的他竟然能夠在1小時內喪做一千次掌上壓，體能比年輕人還要好。獄友又指趙斗淳疑性慾十分旺盛，曾自稱：「聽到監視器的電波聲就能讓我感到興奮」，相信當地市民看到這些傳聞後，又會再度擔心起來。"},{"pid":"86c3b218d86fde8ea74eb874d4c3a47e8df5ec4c","tid":2315687,"uid":128705,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"老閉既聲係咩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5cb2bf3edb671088cb0d432ca3adf421876c86","tid":2315687,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"即係1分鐘要成16下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e4556b95e2ea3820d09161d010d03c9f476e07","tid":2315687,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"如果有部利用性欲黎發電既機器就可以幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cc31edcd6457e6c2c6187b3c54f5f04bba4fde","tid":2315687,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"有d野兩睇 你估佢會唔會比人殺？"},{"pid":"e7af3916febb602da1baf877cd841c7315551963","tid":2315687,"uid":382841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"佢需要既係<br />\n飛機杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de72eccff53f5c3ac316e01ff161ee9c02e7be59","tid":2315687,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"應該送佢暗殺金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{